																},
																"TagText": {
																	"handle": "hf0a185d1g842eg4f61gbe90g03bae5d4d2a1",
																	"value": "If anyone understands an internal voice forcing your hand, I do. But that's not who we are now. We make our own choices, and you made the right one last night.",
